title: War of the Roses: The Self Timed Selfie
description: Caroline started wondering if something's going on with her boyfriend Mitch after she saw a Snapchat he posted with their dog that looked like someone else took it.  His explanation is either the most ridiculous way to take a picture or an insane cover-up of who actually took it.  Is Mitch cheating?
